-space-marines-in-new-warhammer-game-mode-3596784">一项主要新增内容</a>是受<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/warhammer-40000"><em>《战锤 40,000》</em></a>世界启发的游戏模式。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dune-awakening-trailer-reveals-brutal-survival-game-set-on-arrakis-3596838">《沙丘：觉醒》预告片揭示了以厄拉科斯为背景的残酷生存游戏，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
